# Switching

@summary
Coming from Markdown, MDX, Markdoc, Djot, AsciiDoc, reStructuredText,
Typst, Org mode, Textile, or wikitext? Pick a tab below for a practical
mapping into lessmark.

These guides focus on real migration choices: what maps directly, what
should be rewritten as typed blocks, and what has no Lessmark equivalent
because it depends on a renderer, template engine, editor, or runtime.
